name: Dystopia
description:
This was trained on Futagen 2 https://civitai.com/models/4109/futagen

Since it used Protogen 5.3 it's merge here is Dreamlike license

It works well on many checkpoints but NSFW ones turn out the best and takes Loras pretty good.

Trigger word is Dystopia but using it with Post Apocalypse helps.

You should get a nice bizzare image, a ruined landscape with fire. Penises often look like bullets and you'll get amputees with Penises coming off it. Try with a minimal negative prompts like - blurry, b&w, monochrome,extra limbs, young ,anime, watermark, text,

Add ugly too as a lot of the figures are if you don't

I found when using checkpoints that don't nudes or penis as a normal prompt term you can end up getting some cool looking vehicles and creatures and a lot of penis shaped items.

I'll but up a bunch of images, just look at the checkpoints and sampling.

Photorealistic checkpoints do come out nice too when adding more negative prompts.

Use monster instead of man or woman renders strange looking creatures. Adding Sci-Fi to the prompt often creates a wild vehicle or a large city.

You will really have to play with the prompts on this one as you will get crazy results, which sometime are pretty cool looking.
